data.description: Custom built home on 2+ acres! Horses allowed! Open living room with built ins and gas fireplace. Separate formal dining room with tray ceiling and breakfast nook off of kitchen. First floor spacious primary bedroom suite with walk-in closet, separate tub, and shower. Upstairs boasts a large open flex area with 12 ft ceilings, theater room and two additional bonus rooms that could be used as bedrooms. Enjoy outdoor living on the screened porch overlooking the large fully fenced backyard. Three large pastures and one smaller pasture all with electric fencing. Four horse stalls and feed room with storage. Conveniently located 10 minutes to HWY 70 and I95, 35 minutes to Raleigh.
